<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我問你唷，<delay20 />
我把<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />當成賭注，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要不要試著跟我玩場遊戲呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<delay8 />你贏的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就送你<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如何呀？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">好啊好啊！</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">下次吧</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就知道你會這麼說！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那在開始前，<delay20 />我先確認一下，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道遊戲規則嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">跟我說！</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">知道唷</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 />這樣啊？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好吧，<delay8 />我不會勉強你的。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等你有興趣的時候，<delay8 />我們再來玩吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 />那我們就快點開始吧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="NpcShuffle" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我先把卡片洗乾淨<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，<delay20 />接著確認答案吧！</message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你還真聰明耶！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />是你的東西了！<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />收下吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你很擅長這類遊戲吧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />我就把<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 />
送給你這個贏家吧！</message>
	<message label="006_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這次是我贏了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很可惜，禮物不能給你囉。</message>
	<message label="007_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是我徹底輸了呢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />這比我想像的還有趣唷。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有機會再一起玩遊戲吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />看來今天的我<delay8 />
似乎十分受到幸運女神的眷顧呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和你玩遊戲很有趣唷，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />我就知道你會這麼說！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，<delay8 />我們就開始吧。<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你身上的持有物品<delay8 />已經滿了嘛<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣我就沒辦法把禮物送給你了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你先整理一下吧。<delay40 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等你整理好了，我們再來玩，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我來說明規則，<delay20 />你要認真聽唷。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡有<delay8 /><colour id="6" />♥♦<colour id="65535" /><colour id="7" />♠♣<colour id="65535" />四種圖案的卡片。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會從這裡面<delay8 />抽出一張卡片，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你能不能猜中<delay8 />
那張卡片究竟是<delay8 />哪一種圖案呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你猜對了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就按照約定，<delay8 />
把<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />送給你。<pageBreak /><anim id="NpcShuffle" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來，<delay8 />準備好了嗎？<delay20 />要開始囉！<delay frames="40" />
我先把卡片洗乾淨<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 05 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，<delay20 />我抽卡了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這張卡片是<delay8 /><colour id="6" />♥♦<colour id="65535" /><colour id="7" />♠♣<colour id="65535" />之中的哪一種呢？<delay20 />
你來猜看看吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
