	<message label="101_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="6" />♦（方塊）<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="101_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="7" />♠（黑桃）<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="101_d" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="7" />♣（梅花）<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="102_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正確答案是<delay20 /><tag a="140" b="14" arg="0xcd00" />！！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你竟然可以這麼快答對，<delay20 />
真厲害耶！</message>
	<message label="102_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真可惜，<delay20 /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />答案是<tag a="140" b="14" arg="0xcd00" />唷！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個問題是不是<delay20 />有點太難了呢？</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那我來說明規則，<delay8 />你要仔細聽唷。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這裡有<delay20 /><colour id="6" />♥♦<colour id="65535" /><colour id="7" />♠♣<colour id="65535" />四種圖案的卡片。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會從這裡面<delay8 />抽出一張卡片，<delay20 />
